text: emi? Akasalalo mariyu bhumilo unna sakala vastuvulanu vastavaniki allah miku upayuktanga cesadani mariyu ayana bahiranganganu mariyu gopyanganu tana anugrahalanu, miku prasadincadani, miku teliyada? Mariyu prajalalo kondaru elanti jnanam, margadarsakatvam mariyu velugu cupe spastamaina grantham lenide allah nu gurinci vadulade varunnaru
